{"word":"Jahaz","slug":"jahaz","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jahaz</b> <a href=\"#/H3096\">H3096</a> <br/> Called also Jahaza, Jahazah, and Jahzah.<br/> A Levitical city in Reuben, taken from the Moabites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=18'>Jos 13:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21&verse=36'>Jos 21:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=15&verse=4'>Isa 15:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=21'>Jer 48:21</a><br/> Sihon defeated at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=21&verse=23'>Num 21:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=2&verse=32'>Deu 2:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=20'>Jdg 11:20</a>"}]}